data.description: Welcome to a magnificent residence exuding a blend of style and sophistication. On entering, a mesmerizing warm glow emanates from the elegantly embedded fireplace, complementing the neutral color paint scheme, simultaneously recent and timeless. The freshness of the interior paint with recent partial flooring replacement, amplifies the home's overall aesthetic. The main living area seamlessly flows to a spacious deck with new appliances adorning the kitchen. The primary bathroom, designed with an approach to both luxury and practicality, offers double sinks and a separate tub and shower setup for enhanced personal space and convenience. Infused with exquisite detailing and superior craftsmanship, this property ensures a perfect balance between comfort and luxury.
